        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Créer une réservation (responsable uniquement)</p>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LxG3uMb8bBt_y2VR3IDjOIFDIedY4vHt/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-asmbv-red hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
          </svg>
          Ouvrir dans Google Drive
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vidéo 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
      <div class="aspect-video">
        <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EmUsQCJFT6Ch0mfvgjoEaeuq9YQ7YJOl/preview" allow="autoplay" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tutoriel Beach Volley - Partie 2</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">S'inscrire à une session ou un entrainement</p>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EmUsQCJFT6Ch0mfvgjoEaeuq9YQ7YJOl/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-asmbv-red hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
          </svg>
